    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Riot Ride is an <strong>arcade car-combat</strong> game with <strong>roguelike</strong> mechanics. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drive a<strong> weaponized car</strong> through <strong>procedurally </strong>generated levels in a <strong>retro</strong>, <strong>Tron-like</strong> world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect <strong>blueprints </strong>and deliver them back safely while fending off a <strong>variety of hacked vehicles</strong> trying to end your run. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223640/extras/b76e271eb41799b18fbb4995d5f37830.poster.avif?t=1730107325\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223640/extras/b76e271eb41799b18fbb4995d5f37830.webm?t=1730107325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223640/extras/b76e271eb41799b18fbb4995d5f37830.mp4?t=1730107325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Endless play styles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scavenge <strong>weapons</strong> and buy <strong>passive items</strong> from the shop to survive. Use them to <strong>customize</strong> your car <strong>endlessly </strong>to further <strong>personalize your playstyle</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223640/extras/cb3a6aa9ba9a676f67a058e1df3f786c.poster.avif?t=1730107325\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223640/extras/cb3a6aa9ba9a676f67a058e1df3f786c.webm?t=1730107325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223640/extras/cb3a6aa9ba9a676f67a058e1df3f786c.mp4?t=1730107325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenging bosses</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face <strong>increasingly difficult bosses</strong>, each with <strong>unique attack patterns</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223640/extras/cdcad9b6436f781bf5ad58a914486682.poster.avif?t=1730107325\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223640/extras/cdcad9b6436f781bf5ad58a914486682.webm?t=1730107325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223640/extras/cdcad9b6436f781bf5ad58a914486682.mp4?t=1730107325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Perma death</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play, die, learn, and repeat</strong> until you confront the<strong> final villain</strong> in a brutal showdown to finally break free from the simulation. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223640/extras/80de2a4b007b7b1534469e2ab8ef839f.poster.avif?t=1730107325\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223640/extras/80de2a4b007b7b1534469e2ab8ef839f.webm?t=1730107325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223640/extras/80de2a4b007b7b1534469e2ab8ef839f.mp4?t=1730107325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play up to 8 levels (There are 36 levels in the full game)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use up to 17 unique weapons </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test 2 enemy types from the final game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off 2 bosses from the final game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you die, you lose all your progress </p></li></ul>",
